milestones.description: Gavaskar and Azharuddin's 132-run partnership is IND's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 109 between Vengsarkar and Sandeep Patil
Javed Miandad has broken the record for most ODIs (23) as captain for PAK, going past Imran Khan
Gavaskar has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (56) for IND, going past Kapil Dev
